-- Audi to Increase Permanent Staff by 700, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-03-01T18:00:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-01/audi-to-increase-permanent-staff-by-700-handelsblatt-reports.html
Volkswagen AG (VOW) ’s Audi AG unit plans
to offer permanent employment to 700 temporary workers this year
as it increases production in  Germany ,  Handelsblatt  reported
today, citing Thomas Sigi, Audi’s personnel chief.  To contact the reporter on this story:
